data.description: WELCOME HOME! Nicely updated and well maintained throughout.  NO HOA community with sidewalks, parks and convenient to Pungo, shopping, dining, bases, and beaches.  Situated on a spacious lot with the canal to the right, fenced in rear yard, covered porch, patio, gutters, down spouts, wrapped soffits and a NEW roof. You are welcomed in with fresh paint and new LVP flooring that carries from foyer into DR, EIK, and rear hallway/laundry room plus beautiful trim. Living and dining rooms offer optional flex space for multi purposes. Nice FR w/cozy wood FP and ceiling beams. New EIK w/SS appliances, quartz counters, tile backsplash, breakfast area and double door pantry.  Laundry area w/cabinets and rear closet. Spacious BDs w/great closet space - Primary has 2 walk in closets updated vanity and tile flooring. 2nd level full bath w/granite counters and tile flooring. 2 car garage, shed and attic space for storage solutions. Blinds to convey
